Service Details: Offers an informal, 1-hour, weekly drop-in support group for families with babies that discusses various health related topics ranging from nutritional requirements to infant massage to safety and childhood illness.Locations:- Kelowna: Community Health & Services Centre (505 Doyle Avenue, Kelowna)- Rutland: Rutland Health Centre (155 Gray Road, Kelowna)- West Kelowna: West Kelowna Health Centre (106-2300 Carrington Road, West Kelowna)
Dates: 1:30pm - 2:30pm: Rutland, Mon; West Kelowna, Tue; Kelowna, Wed
